{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNSymbolStyleLayer(py)textVariableAnchorOffset","fragments":[{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"textVariableAnchorOffset","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provide an array of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":" locations, each paired with an offset value."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"type":"text","text":" to choose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When present, this property takes precedence over "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textVariableAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textRadialOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"syntax":"json","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"top"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[0, 4]"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"left"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[3, 0]"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This property is only applied to the style if ","type":"text"},{"code":"text","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is non-","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type